Parameters
canonicalizedResource
String String

The canonical path to the signed resource.

resource
String String

The signed services accessible with the service SAS. Possible values include: Blob (b), Container (c), File (f), Share (s). Possible values include: 'b', 'c', 'f', 's'

permissions
String String

The signed permissions for the service SAS. Possible values include: Read (r), Write (w), Delete (d), List (l), Add (a), Create (c), Update (u) and Process (p). Possible values include: 'r', 'd', 'w', 'l', 'a', 'c', 'u', 'p'

iPAddressOrRange
String String

An IP address or a range of IP addresses from which to accept requests.

protocols
Nullable<HttpProtocol> Nullable(Of HttpProtocol)

The protocol permitted for a request made with the account SAS. Possible values include: 'https,http', 'https'

sharedAccessStartTime
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

The time at which the SAS becomes valid.

sharedAccessExpiryTime
Nullable<DateTime> Nullable(Of DateTime)

The time at which the shared access signature becomes invalid.

identifier
String String

A unique value up to 64 characters in length that correlates to an access policy specified for the container, queue, or table.

partitionKeyStart
String String

The start of partition key.

partitionKeyEnd
String String

The end of partition key.

rowKeyStart
String String

The start of row key.

rowKeyEnd
String String

The end of row key.

keyToSign
String String

The key to sign the account SAS token with.

cacheControl
String String

The response header override for cache control.

String String

The response header override for content disposition.

contentEncoding
String String

The response header override for content encoding.

contentLanguage
String String

The response header override for content language.

contentType
String String
